    "summary": "This section defines the document's data visualization conventions, supporting retrieval for the following:\n- **Figures/Chart Types**: Identifies bar charts (柱状图) and line charts (折线图).\n- **Definitions & Metrics**: Specifies that bar charts represent annual market revenue scale, while line charts represent annual market revenue growth rate.\n- **Units**: Clarifies measurement units as 亿元/人民币 (for revenue scale) and % (for growth rate).\n- **Dates/Timeframe**: Indicates data is tracked and displayed annually (每年).\n- **Evidence Types**: Describes quantitative visual evidence used to present market performance.\nAnswers queries regarding chart legends, metric-to-visualization mappings, data units, and annual market reporting formats. No procedures or claims are present."
