    "title": "主要信息与数据趋势",
    "page_range": "4",
    "summary": "This section provides structured quantitative data on market revenue scale (in billion RMB) and annual growth rates from 2021 to 2028. It answers retrieval queries regarding: specific annual market size and growth percentages; historical performance (2021–2024) versus forecasted projections (2025–2028); year-over-year trend shifts, including the 2021 contraction and subsequent recovery; and the projected market trajectory through 2028. Key topics: market revenue trends and growth projections. Dates: 2021–2028. Metrics: market revenue scale (亿元) and annual growth rate (%). Evidence type: structured time-series numerical data with explicit historical and predictive labeling."
  },
  {
    "node_id": "0005",
    "title": "数据趋势分析",
    "page_range": "4",
    "summary": "This section answers questions regarding market revenue and growth rate trends from 2021 to 2028. It specifically covers:\n- **Topics & Entities:** Market revenue scale and annual growth rate.\n- **Dates & Metrics:** 2021 (2769.4亿元, negative growth), 2022 (3.21% growth), 2023 (10.74% peak growth), and 2028 projections (3059.2亿元 revenue, 1.83% growth).\n- **Claims:** Revenue declined after 2021 but resumed annual growth from 2022 onward; growth momentum peaked in 2023 and is forecast to gradually decelerate through 2028.\n- **Evidence Type:** Quantitative historical figures and forward-looking numerical forecasts.\n- **Definitions, Procedures, Tables, Figures:** Not addressed in this section."
  },
