    "summary": "This section provides a figure legend that answers questions regarding the visual definitions, metrics, and subject of an associated chart. It clarifies that the blue bar chart represents the Chinese mobile gaming market's revenue scale (measured in 100 million RMB) and the cyan line chart represents its growth rate (measured in %). It can be used to retrieve definitions for specific chart elements, identify tracked metrics and their units, confirm the core entity and topic (Chinese mobile gaming market), and classify the evidence type as a figure legend. No dates, procedures, claims, or tables are present."
