    "node_id": "0008",
    "title": "总结",
    "page_range": "4-1",
    "summary": "This section enables retrieval of answers to questions concerning:\n• **Topics & Claims:** Historical revenue changes and future growth trends in the China mobile game market, specifically its gradual recovery and stable growth trajectory.\n• **Entities & Data Sources:** Diandian Data (点点数据), corporate financial reports, and expert interviews.\n• **Dates & Timeframes:** Past years, future projections, and potential data adjustments scheduled for Diandian Data’s 2026 reports.\n• **Definitions & Scope:** Statistical scope limited to mobile games launched in mainland China (excludes PC, console, and other hardware platforms; multi-platform titles count only mobile data). Revenue definition restricted to total direct user consumption, explicitly excluding ad monetization and third-party top-ups. This standard governs all subsequent “China revenue” metrics in the report.\n• **Figures & Metrics:** References a chart/figure illustrating revenue fluctuations and growth projections. Core metric is total user consumption revenue.\n• **Evidence Types & Methodology:** Data derived from a synthesis of third-party analytics, official financial disclosures, and expert interviews, calculated using Diandian Data’s proprietary statistical model."
